page.title: 12 CHILDREN OF WEEDON
page.content: *** VICKY *** My name is Vicky.I live with my mum and dad,my pet hamster and our dog.I like money boxes and collect them,at the moment I have twenty three.On Mondays I go to {Majorettes} and on Wednesdays I go to {Brownies}.On Thursdays I go to visit my Grandma.I get up at 06.00,have breakfast at 06.30,dinner at 12.10 and tea at 17.30 hours.I go to bed at 20.30 hours. *** DEBBIE *** My name is Debbie and I live in Equestrian Way,Weedon.My house is built on the site of the old {Royal Pavillions}.I have a 6 year old brother.I am 10 years old and enjoy mathematics best at school.I am good at running and the long jump.I like wearing trousers and shorts as long as they are not flared.
